==ᱚᱛᱱᱚᱜ==
ᱢᱟᱦᱟ ᱥᱟᱢᱩᱱᱫᱽ {{Coord|21.1|N|82.1|E|}} ᱨᱮ ᱢᱮᱱᱟᱜᱼᱟ ᱾<ref>[http://www.fallingrain.com/world/IN/37/Mahasamund.html Falling Rain Genomics, Inc - Mahasamund]</ref> 
